title: Maceo Parker - 1991 - Mo' Roots FLAC
description:
Maceo Parker - 1991 - Mo' Roots

The second Roots installment, Mo' Roots was cut minus Pullen and Collins, leaning a little more toward the instrumental soul side. Three fine originals in conjunction with covers of Ray Charles, Marvin Gaye, Otis Redding, Horace Silver, and Lionel Hampton. (AllMusic)

Track list:
01. Hallelujah, I love Her So
02. Chicken
03. Let's Get It On
04. Hamp's Boogie Woogie
05. Fa Fa Fa (The Sad Song)
06. Jack's Back
07. Sister Sadie
08. Daddy's Home

10. Southwick
